"""csup-dashboard — single-page web view of every supervisor session.

Reads ~/.config/csup/hosts.toml + every project's .codex-supervisor.toml,
captures the last N lines of every pane (locally or via SSH), and serves
them at http://localhost:7777 as a refreshing grid.

Usage:
    csup-dashboard [--port 7777] [--lines 12] [--refresh 0.5]

Hot-reloads project list every poll, so adding a new project only requires
dropping a `.codex-supervisor.toml` in the right place.
"""
